anime_list = anime_list.filter(anime_list.watch_status == 2)
anime_list = anime_list.join(anime_names, anime_list.anime_id == anime_names.anime_id, "inner").drop(anime_names.anime_id)
print((anime_list.count(), len(anime_list.columns)))
anime_list.show()

from pyspark.sql.functions import col, count, sum
from pyspark.sql.window import Window


# Add two new columns to the DataFrame: 
# 1. "total_votes" which counts the number of votes for each anime 
# 2. "user_total_votes" which sums up the number of votes by each user for each anime
anime_list = anime_list.withColumn("anime_total_votes", count("*").over(Window.partitionBy("anime_id"))) \
                   .withColumn("user_total_votes", count("*").over(Window.partitionBy("user_id")))

# Filter the DataFrame to include only the data where 
# 1. the anime has more than 200 votes, and 
# 2. the users has given more than 500 votes to the anime
anime_df_filtered = anime_list.filter((anime_list.anime_total_votes > 400) & (anime_list.user_total_votes > 1000))

# Display the filtered DataFrame
anime_df_filtered.show()

from pyspark.ml.evaluation import RegressionEvaluator, RankingEvaluator
from pyspark.ml.recommendation import ALS
from pyspark.ml.feature import StringIndexer
from pyspark.ml import Pipeline
from pyspark.sql.functions import col

indexer = [StringIndexer(inputCol=column, outputCol=column+"_index") for column in ["user_id", "anime_id"]]
pipeline = Pipeline(stages=indexer)
transformed = pipeline.fit(anime_df_filtered).transform(anime_df_filtered)
transformed.show()

als = ALS(maxIter=15, regParam=0.09, rank=10, userCol="user_id_index", itemCol="anime_id_index", ratingCol="rating", coldStartStrategy="drop", nonnegative=True)
model = als.fit(train_df)

users = train_df.select("user_id_index").distinct()
items = train_df.select("anime_id_index").distinct()
user_item = users.crossJoin(items)
pred_df = model.transform(user_item)

# Remove seen items.
dfs_pred_exclude_train = pred_df.alias("pred").join(
    train_df.alias("train"),
    (pred_df["user_id_index"] == train_df["user_id_index"]) & (pred_df["anime_id_index"] == train_df["anime_id_index"]),
    how='outer'
)

dfs_pred_final = dfs_pred_exclude_train.filter(dfs_pred_exclude_train["train.Rating"].isNull()) \
    .select('pred.' + "user_id_index", 'pred.' + "anime_id_index", 'pred.' + "prediction")

dfs_pred_final.show()

from pyspark.sql.functions import col, row_number, expr

_items_for_user_true = (
            test_df.groupBy("user_id_index")
            .agg(expr("collect_list(" + "anime_id_index" + ") as ground_truth"))
            .select("user_id_index", "ground_truth")
        )
        
_items_for_user_pred = (
            dfs_pred_final.groupBy("user_id_index")
            .agg(F.sort_array(F.collect_list(F.struct("prediction", "anime_id_index")))
            .alias("collected_list")
        )
        .withColumn("pred_list", F.col("collected_list.anime_id_index"))
        .drop("collected_list")
    )
        
_items_for_user_all = _items_for_user_pred.join(
            _items_for_user_true, _items_for_user_pred.user_id_index == _items_for_user_true.user_id_index
        ).drop(_items_for_user_pred.user_id_index)

a = 1

for g in param_grid:
    als = ALS(maxIter=15, userCol="user_id_index", itemCol="anime_id_index", ratingCol="rating", coldStartStrategy="drop", nonnegative=True, **g)
    model = als.fit(train_df)
    
    pred_df = model.transform(user_item)
    
    # Remove seen items.
    dfs_pred_exclude_train = pred_df.alias("pred").join(
        train_df.alias("train"),
        (pred_df["user_id_index"] == train_df["user_id_index"]) & (pred_df["anime_id_index"] == train_df["anime_id_index"]),
        how='outer'
    )
    
    dfs_pred_final = dfs_pred_exclude_train.filter(dfs_pred_exclude_train["train.Rating"].isNull()) \
        .select('pred.' + "user_id_index", 'pred.' + "anime_id_index", 'pred.' + "prediction")

    _items_for_user_true = (
            test_df.groupBy("user_id_index")
            .agg(expr("collect_list(" + "anime_id_index" + ") as ground_truth"))
            .select("user_id_index", "ground_truth")
        )
        
    _items_for_user_pred = (
                dfs_pred_final.groupBy("user_id_index")
                .agg(F.sort_array(F.collect_list(F.struct("prediction", "anime_id_index")))
                .alias("collected_list")
            )
            .withColumn("pred_list", F.col("collected_list.anime_id_index"))
            .drop("collected_list")
        )
            
    _items_for_user_all = _items_for_user_pred.join(
                _items_for_user_true, _items_for_user_pred.user_id_index == _items_for_user_true.user_id_index
            ).drop(_items_for_user_pred.user_id_index)
    
    map_at_5 = evaluations.evaluate(
        _items_for_user_all
    )
    
    print(g)
    print("MAP at 5 = " + str(map_at_5))

    map_at_k.append(map_at_5)
    
    ndcg_at_5 = ndcg_evaluations.evaluate(
    _items_for_user_all
    )
    ndcg_at_k.append(ndcg_at_5)

    print("NDCG at 5 = " + str(ndcg_at_5))
    print()
